column43: The overall aim of this project is to explore%2C characterise and optimise the design of synthetic DNA for digital storage. This set of experiments is for assessing DNA synthesis.%0D%0A%0D%0AThis data is part of a pre-publication release. For information on the proper use of pre-publication data shared by the Wellcome Trust Sanger Institute (including details of any publication moratoria)%2C please see http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sanger.ac.uk%2Fdatasharing%2F
